
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created
    
    Created --> Queued : Submit to Queue
    Queued --> Running : Worker Picked
    
    Running --> Completed : Success
    Running --> Failed : Runtime Error
    
    Created --> Cancelled : User Abort
    Queued --> Cancelled : User Abort
    
    Completed --> [*]
    Failed --> [*]
